    "plan_content": "Here's the complete implementation plan for the **Stepper** compound component:\n\n---\n\n## What will be built\n\n### 3 new files\n| File | Purpose |\n|---|---|\n| `ui/stepper.tsx` | The component library file |\n| `examples/stepper-demo.tsx` | Horizontal demo (3-step wizard) |\n| `examples/stepper-vertical.tsx` | Vertical demo with content panels + Back/Continue |\n\n### 2 registry entry insertions (no existing lines touched)\n- `ui/_registry.ts` → insert `stepper` alphabetically between `spinner` and `switch`\n- `examples/_registry.ts` → insert `stepper-demo` + `stepper-vertical` between `spinner-item` and `switch-demo`\n\n---\n\n## Component Architecture\n\n**Two React contexts** (mirrors `carousel.tsx` pattern):\n- `StepperContext` — root: `value`, `onValueChange`, `orientation`\n- `StepperItemContext` — per step: `value`, `disabled`, `completed`\n\n**8 sub-components** + exported `useStepper` hook, **no new npm dependencies**:\n\n| Component | Element | Role |\n|---|---|---|\n| `Stepper` | `<div>` | Root, `flex-row` or `flex-col` |\n| `StepperItem` | `<div>` | Step wrapper, sets `data-state` |\n| `StepperTrigger` | `<button>` | Calls `onValueChange` on click, `aria-current=\"step\"` |\n| `StepperIndicator` | `<span>` | Visual circle, `aria-hidden`, renders children (number/icon) |\n| `StepperTitle` | `<p>` | Label, color shifts per state |\n| `StepperDescription` | `<p>` | Secondary text |\n| `StepperSeparator` | `<div>` | `h-px flex-1` (horizontal) or `w-px ms-[15px]` (vertical) |\n| `StepperContent` | `<div>` | Returns `null` unless step is active |\n\n**Step states**: `active` | `completed` | `pending` | `disabled` — driven by `data-state` Tailwind selectors\n\n**Layout key**: `ms-[15px]` on the vertical separator centers the 1px line under the 32px (`size-8`) indicator. `ms-10` on `StepperContent` aligns it with the text beside the indicator.",
